sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User
  participant App as React App
  participant Gateway as API Gateway
  participant Auth as Auth Service
  participant SMS as SMS / Mock OTP
  participant DB as auth_db
  User->>App: Open forgot password
  App->>Gateway: POST /api/auth/forgot-password
  Gateway->>Auth: Request reset OTP(phone)
  Auth->>DB: Find active account
  alt Account exists
    Auth->>DB: Store reset OTP with expiry
    Auth->>SMS: Send OTP
    Auth-->>App: OTP sent
  else Account missing or blocked
    Auth-->>App: Generic recovery response
  end
  User->>App: Submit OTP and new password
  App->>Gateway: POST /api/auth/reset-password
  Gateway->>Auth: Verify OTP and password policy
  Auth->>DB: Validate OTP
  alt OTP valid
    Auth->>DB: Update password hash and revoke refresh tokens
    Auth-->>App: Reset success
    App-->>User: Ask user to login again
  else OTP invalid or expired
    Auth-->>App: Reset rejected
    App-->>User: Show validation error
  end
